<A href="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0738205265/ref=mk_del_434213_50">Rudolph 
Tanzi</A>, and scores
		  of others. Participation is limited, creating an environment 
for personal
		  interaction. For more information and to register, call 
1-877-860-7697, or go
		  to 
		  
<A href="http://www.thefutureoflife.com">http://www.thefutureoflife.com</A>. 
<p> 
		Partnering with Amazon.com, <i>Time</i> magazine,
		  along with its editors, conference speakers, and advisory board 
members, has
		  recommended a stunning selection of books--from the classics to 
the cutting
		  edge--that explore all the topics surrounding this momentous 
occasion. After
		  you've browsed through these bestselling and provocative 
titles, you can please
		  your inner scientist further by visiting our 
		  
<A href="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/tg/browse/-/3118561/ref=mk_del_434213_51">50th 
Anniversary of DNA
			 Store</A>. <i>--Brooke Gilbert</i><p> 
	 
